WEBVTT

00:03:59.237 --> 00:04:03.823
that loss, for example,
became fact, fixed --

00:04:03.847 --> 00:04:07.160
necessarily part of my life,

00:04:07.184 --> 00:04:13.300
and I learned that I could no more
reject this fact than reject myself.

00:04:15.173 --> 00:04:17.794
It took me a while,
but I learned it eventually.

00:04:18.572 --> 00:04:21.016
Now, another great thing
about necessary suffering

00:04:21.040 --> 00:04:24.548
is that it is the very thing

00:04:24.572 --> 00:04:29.975
that unites caregiver and care receiver --

00:04:29.999 --> 00:04:31.252
human beings.